      <span class="badge">Ansible Automation Platform</span>
      <h1>Amazon Linux 2023 Daily Demo</h1>
      <p>This web page is served from a <strong>Docker container</strong> that was
         pulled and deployed by an AAP workflow — after the same workflow
         provisioned, patched, hardened, and configured this host.</p>
      <dl>
        <dt>Host</dt><dd><code>{{ inventory_hostname }}</code></dd>
        <dt>OS</dt><dd><code>{{ amzl_release | default(ansible_facts.distribution | default('Amazon') ~ ' ' ~ ansible_facts.distribution_version | default('2023')) }}</code></dd>
        <dt>Container image</dt><dd><code>{{ docker_webserver_image }}</code></dd>
        <dt>Served</dt><dd><span id="now"></span></dd>
      </dl>
